<promed@promedmail.org>
[Although not stated directly in the text of this report, the signs,
symptoms, and circumstances are consistent with an outbreak of norovirus
infection, otherwise known as "winter vomiting disease". Confirmation of the
presumptive diagnosis from an authoritative source would be appreciated. -
Mod.CP]
